@startuml 01-liveness-mismatch-sequence
skinparam dpi 300
title Problem 1 — Liveness Granularity Mismatch (PayGate)\nFalse negative: VM alive, app wedged, probe still passes

actor Client
participant "kubelet\n(liveness probe)" as Kubelet
participant "Cowboy\nlistener :4000" as Cowboy
participant "Finch pool\n(GenServers)" as Finch
participant "Fraud API\n(external)" as Fraud

== Normal traffic ==
Client -> Cowboy: POST /charge
Cowboy -> Finch: checkout worker
Finch -> Fraud: score(charge)
Fraud --> Finch: 200 OK
Finch --> Cowboy: result
Cowboy --> Client: 200 OK

== Dependency hangs (half-open TCP, no timeout) ==
Client -> Cowboy: POST /charge
Cowboy -> Finch: checkout worker
Finch -> Fraud: score(charge)
note right of Fraud: connection half-open\nno response, no timeout
Finch -> Finch: worker blocks indefinitely
note over Finch #ffcccc: all pooled workers blocked\n100% of charges stall

== Liveness probe still passes ==
Kubelet -> Cowboy: TCP connect :4000
Cowboy --> Kubelet: ACK (socket accepted)
note over Kubelet #ffcccc: probe = HEALTHY\nVM alive but app broken\n=> K8s never restarts the pod
@enduml
